            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《SPY×FAMILY 间谍家家酒》的安妮亚向来都人气极高，各厂方都有推出新 Figure，而香港品牌 Threezero 的 「FigZero」系列亦推出「FigZero 安妮亚‧佛杰」 1/6 比例可动 Figure ，当然 Unwire 为大家评测。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205743 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-1-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-1-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-1-507x900.jpg 507w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-1-768x1364.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-1-865x1536.jpg 865w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-1.jpg 901w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Threezero 安妮亚正面</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205744" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-2-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-2-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-2-507x900.jpg 507w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-2-768x1364.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-2-865x1536.jpg 865w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-2.jpg 901w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Threezero 安妮亚背面</p><h2>伊甸学园制服的安妮亚</h2><p>Threezero 的安妮亚高约 16.5 cm，正如 FigZero 系列中的 1/6 比例。而安妮亚是穿著伊甸学园的制服，除了绒布布料外在四肢还有金色较为硬质的布料而成，连脚上的袜子配上黑皮鞋，整体非常精美。而这次 Threezero 说明这次安妮亚拥有 21 个关节，在细小的 Figure 下仍然保持有高可动性，21 个关节绝对足够玩家灵活摆出各种可爱的动作。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205735 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-10-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-10-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-10-507x900.jpg 507w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-10-768x1364.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-10-865x1536.jpg 865w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-10.jpg 901w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲伊甸学园的制服非常精致</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205747" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-13-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-13-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-13-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-13-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-13.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲长袜子配上黑皮鞋</p><h2>21 个关节下所带来的可动性</h2><p>Threezero 的安妮亚头部可正常左右侧望，亦可向上向下观望，而手部只要找到关节位可以大字型举手，手臂可以向上提起约至肩部，亦可水平转动手臂。手掌则是因为有着球体关节，所以可动幅度算大。而腰部因为受制于衣服的缘故，只能作小幅度的可动。而大腿可抬起至约 90 度，小腿则可以向后屈至 90 度，最后脚掌可以上下左右扭动。在调整关节的时候大致顺畅，可动性方面可收货。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1205746 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-15-392x580.jpg" alt="" width="392" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-15-392x580.jpg 392w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-15-608x900.jpg 608w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-15-768x1136.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-15-1038x1536.jpg 1038w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-15.jpg 1081w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 392px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲手臂的可动范围</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205733 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-14-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-14-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-14-675x900.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-14-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-14-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-14.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可动性非常方便</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205742" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-16-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-16-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-16-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-16-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-16.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲脚部即使弯曲也没有穿崩位</p><h2>奇美拉公仔登场增加可玩性</h2><p>在配件上给了一个「奇美拉」公仔，作为安妮亚贴身可爱玩偶。外观上跟动画一样以粉色和水蓝色为主，头顶上亦有黄色的角，而下半身亦有像蛇一样的尾部，除了上色非常仔细还有著少量的可动性，手部与头部可以作为轻微小幅度可动，配合安妮亚手形就可以做出抱偶的动作。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205736 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-11-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-11-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲奇美拉公仔</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205737" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-12-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-12-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-12-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-12.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一起使用的话就更可爱</p><h2>多种表情脸部更换</h2><p>这次有提供额外四个表情共五个脸部可以更换，这次头雕由知名原型师高木亮雕制。除了原本收录在 Figure 的普通微笑表情，遇到难题的惊讶震惊表情、超级经典的奸笑脸、还有脸红开心的微笑表情以及最可爱挖苦挖苦的期待表情。换脸方法相当简单只需要将头部打开替换即可，在各种表情下定能满足动画下出现的安妮亚。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205738 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲五种表情脸部任意更换</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205741" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-8-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-8-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-8-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ ⌓‿⌓</p><h2>配合手部配件完美还原动画</h2><p>除了原本在盒上的手部零件，配合握拳、放松、抱娃娃及指向等共五款可换零件，即可为安妮亚的可玩性锦上添花。在各种面部与手部的配合，让很多造型都能够还原在动画上的经典动作。不论是期待动作或是握拳惊讶表情，都能一一还原在玩家眼中。唯一要留意的是，手部因为采用球体关节，重复替换可能会出现磨损等情况。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205739 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲合共五款手型</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205740" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-7-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配合表情绝对有趣</p><h2>总结：ワクワク 值得拥有</h2><p>这次 threezero 的安妮亚惊喜十足，原本担心 FigZero 系列的比例会让整体身形十分奇怪，不过在上手的过程还是非常满意，整体也是比较自然。而当中的服装外观也是诚意十足，除了外观设计讲究也尽量还原动画的细节。在各种表情下配合不同的手部配件，可做出多种可爱的动作，对于喜爱《SPY×FAMILY》的 Fans 来讲根本没有拒绝的余地。而原本只有三款表情也增加至五款表情，光是这个表情就值得推荐给大家，以这个价钱也没什么好挑剔，所以一起「挖苦挖苦」吧！</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205745 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-9-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-9-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-9-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲设计相当到位</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1205748" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/threezero-anya-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲头部特写</p><p style="text-align: center;">▲整体还真的很好了</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

